data.description: Welcome home to this charming 3 bedroom, 2 full bath ranch in a prime location! Home  features a welcoming open floor plan with stylish vinyl plank flooring in the living room and  bedrooms. The main bathroom was beautifully renovated just last year. Step outside and enjoy  the cute covered front porch, perfect for relaxing with a cup of coffee or a good book. Plus, you'll love the convenience of a huge detached oversized garage, providing ample storage space and room for all your projects. This home is ideally situated, offering easy access to Interstate 70 and downtown Indianapolis. Seller is offering assistance in a rate buy down, so don't let the interest rates cause you to miss the opportunity to make this delightful property your home!
